\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Relative performance gain of SB-GRPO compared to the M-GRPO baseline. The significant improvements in \textit  {Intermediate Algebra} (+4.88\%) and \textit  {Precalculus} (+5.68\%) demonstrate the effectiveness of semantic balancing in complex reasoning, while the stability in \textit  {Algebra} confirms that the Heuristic Confidence Gate prevents correction bias in simpler tasks.}}{10}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:delta}{{2}{10}{Relative performance gain of SB-GRPO compared to the M-GRPO baseline. The significant improvements in \textit {Intermediate Algebra} (+4.88\%) and \textit {Precalculus} (+5.68\%) demonstrate the effectiveness of semantic balancing in complex reasoning, while the stability in \textit {Algebra} confirms that the Heuristic Confidence Gate prevents correction bias in simpler tasks}{figure.2}{}}
